{"tid":2315574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"23 歲技術員認襲警還押候判　辯方：到示威現場湊熱鬧　驚慌下推開女警","createTime":"2020-12-07T09:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T09:54:05.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8267f780e0fe3e1972363996325e3e71b11d6777","tid":2315574,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"有網民去年 11 月 2 日於多區發起集會及「快閃」示威；其中在旺角，一名 23歲技術員被指推跌女警，被控一項襲警罪，他今（7日）於九龍城裁判法院認罪，辯方求情時指被告當晚出於好奇，前往案發地點山東街湊熱鬧；他在警員驅散下跟著人群逃跑，在驚慌下推開女警，是「非常錯的行為」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，根據案例有關控罪性質一般判刑是即時監禁，法庭亦要考慮判刑的阻嚇性和相稱性；有關案件牽涉襲警，可幸的是女警的傷勢並非嚴重，加上被告年輕、選擇認罪，將為他先索取背景報告及勞教中心報告，不排除任何方式的處分，<span class=\"red\">押後至 12 月 21 日判刑</span>，被告須還押懲教署看管。"},{"pid":"521ee331dd563e02d530bb4fe818c798a6846089","tid":2315574,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-2-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-23-%E6%AD%B2%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%93%A1%E8%AA%8D%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E5%88%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%B9%8A%E7%86%B1%E9%AC%A7-%E9%A9%9A%E6%85%8C%E4%B8%8B%E6%8E%A8%E9%96%8B%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-2-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-23-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25B9%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25AC%25A7-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2585%258C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=13bdfbc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-2-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-23-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%2593%2